 you see - I think they were both fairly - good. Mother mainly, well maybe - with being with them all I think that would be - she would be - play the more - important part I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11363695 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10627816\charrsid2896712 When you had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
