inary I think, nothing to speak about. Of course the - at that time you know we - mother used to make these mistletoe you know. Two or three bundles, you know, these bowlers that the youngster use now. She used to - put one within the other and one round 
the middle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11363695 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10627816\charrsid2896712 Where did you hang those?
