Well there was - you know, the general run of - of childrens stories, we usually keep a few of them. And - I don't know, there was nothing special. Nothing special. Oh - sometimes - Bobby Burn's poems.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11363695 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10627816\charrsid2896712 Did your mother read to you at all?
\par 
