now then clubs, there wasn't any up at Stanhope. But there was at Shildon. He was a club member at Shildon, but - at Stanhope there was - there were no club when we were there. And if he attended the pub it would only be - occasionally - maybe only Sunday
 evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11363695 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10627816\charrsid2896712 Would you say he attended a club regularly? When he was at Shildon?
