Well now then - of course I was - you know - Charlie died. Well - the next was his brother, Tom, and - Frank Beatty, Tom Beatty, Tommy Crawford - Jack Crawford.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11363695 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10627816\charrsid2896712 These were all children who lived near you were they?
