u could make beer, and it was - hops and - barley and this sort of thing. I - aye, you bought them in a box you know. It was all completer, ready for the - putting in the pan with the yeast and - 'cos you used to put yeast in the pan, a bit of sugar and -
 and so forth. Put them in the dish and let them stand with a piece of yeast on. And then take it off, and put it it the - in the bottles. It was all right and all.
