 garden would grow. Beans, peas, lettuce, scallions. Beetroot. Now what else is there, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7290276\charrsid2896712 c}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10627816\charrsid2896712 elery, aye, celery, leeks, onions. I've finished now, I've finished.
