Well - no, he was more occupied by - enjoying his food was Lance but after he - after he - he used to say can I leave, can I leave, and he used - yes, you can leave the table and then - get down then and - aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11363695 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10627816\charrsid2896712 
Could he choose what he wanted to eat from what was cooked or did he have to have a bit of everything?
