Oh - high chair at first, yes, and then - after that he used to come to the table, I should think he would be about - oh he would be three of four. Aye, four I would think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11363695 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10627816\charrsid2896712 Where would his high chair be, was it at the table with you?
