 have, we had piano, we had a organ. Aye, our Lance - our Lance learned to play the organ, and Gwen learned to play the piano.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11363695 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10627816\charrsid2896712 Did you play anything at all?
