h - aye, we used to have a bicycle game. Well - instead of a counter you had a bicycle, and - you used to take a run in the country on the bicycle and when you come to an obstacle you had - what ever obstruction it was you either had to stay for the loss 
of -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11363695 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10627816\charrsid2896712 On the same idea as snakes and ladders?
