s
s - 'course - this interchange privilege ticket was set away for to the station - at - Normanton of Kirkby Stephen, Tebay, sometimes you could - you could get one at York. I've known them being got at York but you used to - give three days notice for an i
nterchange. And then you got this privilege ticket and you just put it in at the booking office and show your pass and you got issued with the ticket.
